name: BIRTH / DEATH
description: From birth to death we all experience an endless sequence of moments that culminate as the preservation of the ego; every journey, a subjective swim within the sea of human knowledge that becomes the collective objectivity. We think we are the alpha and the omega of our consciousnesses. We make choices every moment of every second of every minute of every day. Everything around us is a story; we create the meaning. In the short window of existence we all are gifted, our journeys diverge like quantum bubbles moving through particle fields in the fabric of spacetime; popping once we die, our life's energy transferred back to the source.
